@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
actor "Delivery Service" as DS
control "Payment Gateway" as PG
actor "Seller" as S
participant "Admin" as A
participant "Customer" as C
DS -> C : Apply Coupon
S --> DS : Make Payment
A -> S : Manage Inventory
C -> A : Add To Cart
PG -> C : Write Review
note over C : processing write review
@enduml